data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and style in this growing and serene Vine Grove neighborhood! This 4-bedroom, 3 bath home features hardwood and tile flooring, an outdoor deck for entertaining, a Great room with a vaulted ceiling that displays great natural light, a walk-out basement family room, and a spacious backyard. This home offers ideal space for relaxation and gatherings. Convenient access that is minutes away from schools, shopping, dining, and Fort Knox, this home is perfect for Modern living.
